    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有报道称博士伦正在考虑出售，其股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/bausch-lomb-soars-on-report-that-it-s-exploring-a-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博士伦公司 (Bausch + Lomb Corp.) 的股价出现历史最大涨幅，此前有报道称，这家眼保健公司正考虑出售自己，以摆脱负债累累的母公司的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/bausch-lomb-soars-on-report-that-it-s-exploring-a-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 13:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德对债券发出警告，称对美联储利率的押注过度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/blackrock-warns-on-bonds-saying-fed-rate-cut-bets-are-overdone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司策略师将对短期美国国债的持仓评级从增持转为减持，称市场押注的美联储降息幅度不太可能实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/blackrock-warns-on-bonds-saying-fed-rate-cut-bets-are-overdone</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
