      <title>西非数百万人受洪水影响后将迎来更多降雨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/west-africa-braces-for-more-rain-after-floods-displace-millions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西非本周将迎来更多暴雨，该地区发生洪灾，仅 2024 年一年就有至少 230 万人因水位上涨而流离失所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/west-africa-braces-for-more-rain-after-floods-displace-millions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 10:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
